A fan site has spotted nine job listings on Apple's official recruitment site .
It includes listings for an iOS battery life software engineer, a power system engineer and battery pack engineering manager .
Apple said it takes 1.5 hours to charge the Watch to 80% and 2.5hours for a full charge .
The company said battery life is based on 18 hours of use .
This includes 90 notifications, 90 notifications and 45 minutes of app use .